```bash
sudo chown -R $(whoami) /usr/local/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai
```

```bash
mkdir -p ~/.npm-global
npm config set prefix '~/.npm-global'
# Add to ~/.bashrc: export PATH=~/.npm-global/bin:$PATH
npm i -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code
```
